title: Ranked Team
body:
G'day,

We are a group of mature gamers in our late 20's looking for mature guys to share some ranked with. We range from Diamond to Gold. 

It would be preferable if you are 18 and above. No raging towards team mates. Also enjoys a good laugh over skype. 

Looking for all positions. 

Currently have a roster of 5 players, however looking to add more spots to allow regular games if others are unable to play. 

You can add me in game as

"Best Indian Fid" 

Cheers.
